---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for brandonjohnson.dev." canonical="/privacy">
  <section class="article-page">
    <div class="container article-shell prose">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="muted">Effective date: April 22, 2026</p>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>This privacy policy describes how brandonjohnson.dev collects, uses, and handles information when you visit or interact with this personal portfolio website.</p>
      <h2>Information I Collect</h2>
      <p>When you use the contact form or email link, I collect the information you submit, which may include your name, email address, and message content. Basic technical information may also be logged by the hosting provider.</p>
      <h2>How I Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>I use submitted information to respond to inquiries, understand general traffic patterns, and maintain site security. I do not sell, rent, or share personal information for marketing purposes.</p>
      <h2>Cookies and Analytics</h2>
      <p>This static site uses minimal functionality and does not rely on advertising cookies or cross-site tracking.</p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, reach out via the contact page.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
